follow me into the family business.

00:38:05.074 --> 00:38:08.244
I've been to funerals
with more life than this gala.

00:38:09.537 --> 00:38:12.706
We're about to heat things up
with a student dance routine.

00:38:12.707 --> 00:38:15.750
And then we'll call you to the stage
for some brief remarks.

00:38:15.751 --> 00:38:20.089
And finally, I'll whisk you to my office
to complete the pesky paperwork.

00:38:24.885 --> 00:38:26.887
[operatic singing in distance]

00:38:34.979 --> 00:38:37.522
Have your moths
