00:39:10.139 --> 00:39:12.098
[Gabrielle gasps] Ajax!

00:39:12.099 --> 00:39:14.434
Don't worry, Dort can't hurt you anymore.

00:39:14.435 --> 00:39:16.270
Come on, show's about to start.

00:39:18.272 --> 00:39:19.272
[music trails off]

00:39:19.273 --> 00:39:20.649
[exhales steadily]

00:39:22.693 --> 00:39:25.362
