00:44:04.975 --> 00:44:07.226
I held Bianca's mother hostage

00:44:07.227 --> 00:44:10.104
to force her to Siren Hester Frump

00:44:10.105 --> 00:44:12.357
to donate her fortune.

00:44:12.358 --> 00:44:13.483
[outraged gasps]

00:44:13.484 --> 00:44:15.319
[student] Are you out of your mind?

00:44:16.654 --> 00:44:20.531
Also, I promised
my Morning Song stooge, Gideon,

00:44:20.532 --> 00:44:22.492
that I would split the money.

00:44:22.493 --> 00:44:24.286
But I'm not big into sharing,

00:44:25.829 --> 00:44:28.247
so now he's a pile of ash in my fireplace,

00:44:28.248 --> 00:44:30.042
and I'm keeping all the cash.

00:44:30.542 --> 00:44:32.169
[audience clamoring]

00:44:36.256 --> 00:44:37.257
Oh, boy.

00:44:39.176 --> 00:44:40.844
- [Dort] All right!
- [Morticia gasps]

00:44:42.721 --> 00:44:45.557
I'm walking out of here,
or the Siren's toast!

00:44:48.102 --> 00:44:50.145
Back off! Stand back!

00:44:50.896 --> 00:44:51.980
I mean it!

00:44:54.566 --> 00:44:56.025
[dramatic music swells]

00:44:56.026 --> 00:44:57.569
[Gomez gasps]

00:45:00.781 --> 00:45:01.782
[Ajax] Dort!

00:45:03.117 --> 00:45:04.910
[hissing]

00:45:19.174 --> 00:45:21.217
[dramatic music crescendos, trails off]

00:45:21.218 --> 00:45:22.428
[crowd gasps]

00:45:24.680 --> 00:45:26.557
[delighted laughter]

00:45:27.391 --> 00:45:28.726
Oh, bravo!

00:45:30.811 --> 00:45:33.313
Now that's what I call a thrilling climax.

00:45:38.193 --> 00:45:40.695
[Bianca] I don't know
how you hacked my Siren song,

00:45:40.696 --> 00:45:42.113
but thank you.

00:45:42.114 --> 00:45:44.241
I'm not the one you should be thanking.

00:45:49.830 --> 00:45:51.915
I owe you one, Ajax.

00:45:55.753 --> 00:45:57.755
You really rocked his world.

00:46:00.048 --> 00:46:03.384
I'm looking forward
to having your company this summer.

00:46:03.385 --> 00:46:06.971
It will give me an excuse
to decamp the bats from the guest wing.

00:46:06.972 --> 00:46:10.850
After the vile comment you made
about my father, I'm canceling my plans.

00:46:10.851 --> 00:46:12.352
I've lost my ability.

00:46:12.978 --> 00:46:14.979
Does that make me less of an Outcast?

00:46:14.980 --> 00:46:17.899
Don't be ridiculous.
You're just going through a phase.

00:46:17.900 --> 00:46:20.276
My father has many infuriating habits,

00:46:20.277 --> 00:46:22.946
but when it comes to being an Outcast,
there's none finer.

00:46:23.447 --> 00:46:25.156
If you would like me to reconsider,

00:46:25.157 --> 00:46:29.620
you must make a very sizable donation
to Nevermore in his honor.

00:46:30.662 --> 00:46:32.455
Are you resorting to emotional blackmail?

00:46:32.456 --> 00:46:34.416
There's nothing emotional about it.

00:46:35.167 --> 00:46:36.710
It's just blackmail.

00:46:37.836 --> 00:46:40.088
[indulgent laughter] Done.

00:46:41.173 --> 00:46:43.090
Only you could throw a gala

00:46:43.091 --> 00:46:47.136
that begins with a fiery murder
and ends with a shattering death.

00:46:47.137 --> 00:46:49.305
- Well played, my dear.
- You're not upset?

00:46:49.306 --> 00:46:51.307
Almost being conned
out of my entire fortune

00:46:51.308 --> 00:46:53.976
was the biggest rush I've had in years.

00:46:53.977 --> 00:46:55.813
I actually feel alive.

00:46:56.438 --> 00:46:58.899
[mischievous music playing]

00:47:11.787 --> 00:47:14.121
Wednesday! Isaac... he's here.

00:47:14.122 --> 00:47:16.333
- Where?
- At the Nevermore graveyard.

00:47:17.709 --> 00:47:18.710
Pugsley.

00:47:19.586 --> 00:47:20.879
Where's Pugsley?

00:47:24.466 --> 00:47:26.051
[eerie music playing]

00:47:32.766 --> 00:47:33.767
[Pugsley chuckles]

00:47:41.149 --> 00:47:42.860
Hello, old friend.

00:47:44.778 --> 00:47:45.654
Slurp?

00:47:46.947 --> 00:47:47.990
Is that you?

00:47:55.706 --> 00:47:56.790
Pugsley,

00:47:58.500 --> 00:48:00.127
I hate to ask but...

00:48:02.170 --> 00:48:03.547
I need your help.

